?=C2=A0
Certainly, if you=E2=80=99d redirected funding from Graphics Processing Uni=
ts (GPUs) because better graphics in video games weren=E2=80=99t really imp=
ortant, or from all of the blogs and Reddits and Twitters and cat pic sites=
