in the middle of the AI renaissance we are today.=C2=A0
My suspicion is that while a lot of the past few decades=E2=80=99 innovatio=
n in the world of Bits doesn=E2=80=99t feel like it directly increases the =
potential for happiness as much as the wave of innovation in Atoms that sta=
