 a happy meal.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16px;=
 line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>Biotech has gotten so advanc=
ed that disease isn&#8217;t really a thing anymore. People commonly live to=
 200 or 300 years old, and rumor is, the cap is about to be lifted entirely=
=2E For many, it already effectively is &=
#8211; anyone can upload their brain=
&#8217;s neural patterns into the cloud and download them into robots, a la=
 Robin Hanson&#8217;s </span><em><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/4=
